使第三人得之者，亦同。\r\n前二項之未遂犯罰之。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/MLDM/110%2c%e8%8b%97%e7%b0%a1%2c792%2c20211026%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"MLDM,110,苗簡,792,20211026,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"苗簡","JNO":"792","JDATE":"20211026","JTITLE":"詐欺"}